The paper discusses deep learning approaches for question answering over knowledge bases, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of several sub-fields in computer science. "cs.CL" (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category as it specifically deals with natural language processing tasks such as question answering. "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) and "cs.LG" (Machine Learning) are also likely as they cover topics related to deep learning architectures. "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) is another possible sub-category as the paper deals with retrieving information from a knowledge base. Finally, "cs.DB" (Databases) is a less likely but still possible sub-category as the paper deals with knowledge bases, which are a type of database.
